'''Caitlin''' is a waitress at Flanner's who was present when it burned down.

==History==
Caitlin helped [[Chris (Let It Burn)|Chris]] with his sixth birthday presentation of the day, but was unaware that the match he used and then threw away reignited in the trash and caused a large fire which ultimately burned the whole building down.

==Career==
She was a waitress at Flanner's until it burned down.

==Notes and Trivia==
*She's named after a friend of [[Barbara Friend|Barbara Kaye Friend]] who once almost burned their apartment down.
